      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom condition. This meticulously maintained example represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every service milestone has been documented, ensuring this vehicle performs with the same precision it did the day it left the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality, this is an investment-grade acquisition that delivers an unparalleled driving experience.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
